    <h1>Youngest director</h1>

<% date = Director.where.not({:dob => nil}).all.order({:dob => :asc}).at(-1).dob %>
<% formatted_date = date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>

<p>The youngest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%= Director.where.not({:dob => nil}).all.order({:dob => :asc}).at(-1).id %>"><%= Director.where.not({:dob => nil}).all.order({:dob => :asc}).at(-1).name %></a>, born on <%= formatted_date %>.</p>

<p>(<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>


<ol>
<% Director.all.each do |name| %>

<li><%= name.name %></li>


<%end%>
</ol> 
